content:
Program Management

Group program participants by cohort to better track the results for individuals or the whole cohort. Save time with the new Program Management Home Page. Quickly remove one or more participants from all upcoming benefit sessions.

Remove Participants from Upcoming Scheduled Sessions
When using Program Management, on one benefit session, you can now remove the participants from upcoming sessions in one shot.

Group Program Participants into Cohorts
Move a group of participants through the program together to make sure that individuals don’t slip through the cracks. Compare current cohorts with previous ones or an individual’s progress against that of the rest of their cohort.

Get a Comprehensive View of Your Program Delivery
Use the Program Management Home Page to track if programs are moving towards their targets, see new inbound referrals, get a snapshot of your programs and benefits, and add participants to upcoming sessions.

New Objects in Program Management
Do more with the new Program Management objects.

Updated Program Management Connect API
Make the most of the updated Program Management Connect APIs.
title: Program Management Updates in Salesforce Summer '24
